================================================================================
                              ADDRESS MAP
================================================================================

AXI ADDRESS MAP
------------------------------

0x0000_0000 -> 0x0000_FFFF   AXI SRAM

0x1000_0000 -> 0x1000_FFFF   AXI->APB BRIDGE



APB PERIPHERAL MAP
------------------------------

0x1000_0000   GPIO
0x1000_1000   UART
0x1000_2000   SPI



GPIO REGISTER MAP
------------------------------

0x00   GPIO_DATA
0x04   GPIO_DIR



UART REGISTER MAP
------------------------------

0x00   TXDATA
0x04   RXDATA
0x08   STATUS
0x0C   CONTROL



SPI REGISTER MAP
------------------------------

0x00   TXDATA
0x04   RXDATA
0x08   STATUS
0x0C   CONTROL



